items.text: The lunch menu was mostly burger s and finger food. Tried the James Brown burger and was pretty good. The balcony area although small was nice and relaxing
Good outdoor for drink when weather is good
Naughty fries is the bomb! The fries is the best!! Ordered a burning man burger and it was just okay. Nothing special.
Burgers at three buns are great. Burning man was good. Cool vibes, nice atmosphere, good music. Oh and homemade soda.
One of the only cozy and beautiful modern restaurant/bar interiors in Singapore. Not sterile or fake.

Cool place with great burgers, had a spicy one that was amazing. 3 levels, 1st level is restaurant, 2nd is bar with dim lighting and cool decor, 3rd is rooftop bar.
Good ambience however the burgers are not worth the value.  You can get better burgers at Burger King.
Crowded at rooftop for a tues night . Interesting interior. Tues special - Shabba burger. Not much choices for finger food.
The Potato Head brand has become easily one of the trendiest in southeast Asia. Decor is gorgeous, service is ok. High-end, no less than S$25 per cocktail. Burgers and Naughty fries are to die for.
I cannot describe how good the burgers are here. Best in SG.
Average burgers with more flash than substance. Thankfully the drinks are decent and things get better upstairs. Love the friendly bar staff esp CUT bar alumni Erwan. Nice rooftop bar too.
the fries was worth it, coffee was too much of an acidity that didn't quite match up to the standards. overall atmosphere is worth paying a visit for, could imagine the bar to be great at night..

Grab drinks at a quirky Balinese bar.

Go all out with the Truff Ryder! It's GOOD! Have it on the roof with an IPA. Cocktails not great.

Upstairs on the roof for drinks. The hamburgers are wonderful.

Best burger in town!

Rooftop. bar. space.
